  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may have heard of it, tales, whispers, warnings.. But have you ever considered participating in a society?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Well now's your chance, put on your clown suit and see how long you and your friends would survive in this chaotic realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or with your friends as a group up to 4. Use proximity voice chat, text, or vague emoting to communicate with other clowns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore every strange part of society including Grocery Shopping, Kindergarten, the Park, Crossing the Street, Fast Food Jobs, the Coal Mines, Birthday Parties and many more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against the bizarre denizens like Consumers, Blind Dates, Ducks, Teachers, Giant Brains, Gremlins or the seemingly harmless Normie.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The further you travel into society the more dangerous it becomes but also, better rewards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different events and locations will randomly appear depending on your karma, collected relics, difficulty and actions you take.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain experience and money that will help you on future treks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the Neet Mobile to travel, store equipment and relics, discuss strategy or take a break from the horror.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bottom Text</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may have heard of it, tales, whispers, warnings.. But have you ever considered participating in a society?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Well now's your chance, put on your clown suit and see how long you and your friends would survive in this chaotic realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or with your friends as a group up to 4. Use proximity voice chat, text, or vague emoting to communicate with other clowns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore every strange part of society including Grocery Shopping, Kindergarten, the Park, Crossing the Street, Fast Food Jobs, the Coal Mines, Birthday Parties and many more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against the bizarre denizens like Consumers, Blind Dates, Ducks, Teachers, Giant Brains, Gremlins or the seemingly harmless Normie.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The further you travel into society the more dangerous it becomes but also, better rewards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different events and locations will randomly appear depending on your karma, collected relics, difficulty and actions you take.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain experience and money that will help you on future treks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the Neet Mobile to travel, store equipment and relics, discuss strategy or take a break from the horror.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bottom Text</p>",
